CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: SolarWinds Corp is a provider of information technology (IT), and infrastructure management software. Products and services offered by the company include network management, system management, database management, IT security, and IT help desk, among others. It sells a comprehensive portfolio of IT management products that are designed for ITOps, DevOps, SecOps, and IT security professionals. Geographically, the firm generates a majority of its revenue from the United States of America.
